<h2 id="graph">Graph</h2>
<p>Since it is always a ULM in each time interval then in a $x-t$ graph the curve is a straight line in each interval. Fig. <a href="#fig:sfulm-1d-ABCDE-x-t">2</a> wil show the graph.</p>

